
  Usage: Hillary [options]

  Options:

    -h, --help                output usage information
    -V, --version             output the version number
    -q, --question [Vraag]    Question generation: i.e. Type -> "-q Hillary"
    -a, --answer [Antwoord]   Answer generation: i.e. Type -> "-a Hillary"
    -w, --width [Breedte]     Width of the answer: i.e. Type -> "60"
    -s, --sentences [Aantal]  Number of sentences (usable when genereating an answer): i.e. Type -> "5"

